            <thetext>Use Case:
A app developer downloads the new SDK and changes the SDK path in his config.json to the new SDK. Unfortunately, he does not know about the migration job and therefore updates his app himself without the automatic migration script.

For these use case, it might be handy to have a simple hint during any build job as soon as the SDK version has been updated. This hint should contain a pointer to the migration job and how to use it.</thetext>
